{
  "stem": "11272.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] You know, it's very difficult to think back now what the thoughts were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember somehow or other-- I wanted to make sure that I see my brother Sam, somehow or other, that I see some of my friends-- that somehow, I stay alive, that I keep my commitment to father and mother.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because not too many of us made it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw too many of my friends just give up because they couldn't make it anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And once we got to Gleiwitz, I saw my brother Sam again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just-- his group was marched past me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how I find him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that gave me a lot of courage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That gave me so much-- [SIGHS] so much needed mental boost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they put us into open, coal-carrying cars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, the difference between that-- there's no top, absolutely no top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was made out of steel, sides and bottom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, you're talking about December and January, where the temperature normally is 10 below zero there at night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when you go 10, 15, 20, 30, 40, 50 miles an hour in the-- in the train, and the wind goes against you in maybe another 20 miles an hour, it can get 40, 50 below zero.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a lot of my friends just became icicles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- as they were standing, they froze to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, they were collapsing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So a lot of us were able to hide under their bodies a little bit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But that trip, even though it lasted only maybe five, six days, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] has left an indelible mark on my mind that, that cannot be described in any way, shape, or form.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
